ake/releases/latest/download/CodeRunner_x64.msi\" rel=\"nofollow\">Windows</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/tw93/Pake/releases/latest/download/CodeRunner_x86_64.deb\" rel=\"nofollow\">Linux</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.fliggy.com/upic/8A3FfQ.png\"/></td>\n<td><img class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.fliggy.com/upic/EB1OYP.jpg\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Flomo\n            <a href=\"https://github.com/tw93/Pake/releases/latest/download/Flomo.dmg\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mac</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/tw93/Pake/releases/latest/download/Flomo_x64.msi\" rel=\"nofollow\">Windows</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/tw93/Pake/releases/latest/download/Flomo_x86_64.deb\" rel=\"nofollow\">Linux</a>\n</td>\n<td>Loop\n            <a href=\"https://github.com/tw93/Pake/releases/latest/download/Loop.dmg\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mac</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/tw93/Pake/releases/latest/download/Loop_x64.msi\" rel=\"nofollow\">Windows</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/tw93/Pake/releases/latest/download/Loop_x86_64.deb\" rel=\"nofollow\">Linux</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/k/30/RoUSUf.png\"/></td>\n<td><img class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://cdn.fliggy.com/upic/ajRw5F.png\"/></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2>更多了解可见</h2>\n<p>Pake - 支持三端平台的一键网页打包桌面客户端程序：<a href=\"https://zhiqiu.vercel.app/post/RQpFHJhmC/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://zhiqiu.vercel.app/post/RQpFHJhmC/</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/936901","replies":22,"created_ts":1683029392,"created":"20:09:52","title":"👩🏻‍🍼 Pake 2.0 - 利用 Rust 轻松构建轻量级桌面应用","author":"tw93","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tw93","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/164c/eb62/109043_mini.png?m=1665799887"},{"id":936848,"node":"macOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598","description":"<p>本来还以为是硬盘问题，结果朋友也遇到了</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/936848","replies":22,"created_ts":1683002909,"created":"12:48:29","title":"m1 Mac 外接移动硬盘&固态因供电问题掉盘","author":"will42","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/will42","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b3e2959d6ceac6f5636887517cd659dc?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":936832,"node":"NAS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1614702882","description":"<p>最近新入门 PT ，有个新手考核，有点疑问：</p>\n<h3>环境</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>无公网 IP ，v4/v6 都没有。</li>\n<li>资源下载后，一直持续做种 12 小时如下。\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://article.biliimg.com/bfs/article/9d03d8bbe6c9c215dc1bc0263599cebba3894c52.jpg\"/></li>\n</ol>\n<h3>结果</h3>\n<p>如下，平均做种时间明显对不上：\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://article.biliimg.com/bfs/article/74d25334d2fb1c66a5b0c9d2f509255bf75a4b0e.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>各位 PT 老玩家能解答下吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/936832","replies":22,"created_ts":1682996894,"created":"11:08:14","title":"PT 新手考核疑问-平均做种时间不增长","author":"cesign","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/cesign","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ac93/efee/607365_mini.png?m=1677721349"}]